# Code owners — auto-requested as reviewers on matching PRs.
# See https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-permissions-and-collaborations/managing-repository-settings/about-code-owners

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
*                       @qatoolist

# Security- and supply-chain-sensitive areas get explicit ownership so changes
# to the trust boundary always route through the maintainer.
/.github/                @qatoolist
/.goreleaser.yaml        @qatoolist
/Dockerfile              @qatoolist
/kernel/authz/           @qatoolist
/kernel/auth/            @qatoolist
/kernel/secrets/         @qatoolist
/kernel/apikey/          @qatoolist
/kernel/audit/           @qatoolist
/migrations/             @qatoolist
